(11434, 478, 'artist_details_0_artist_bio', 'Ausdance Victoria is the voice for dance in Victoria. We lead, support and champion all things dance.    Ausdance Victoria loves dance and we want to share our love of dance with you!    Ausdance Victoria exists to support, enrich, advance and advocate dance in all its forms. We provide services, advice, classes, workshops and professional development to the dance sector as a whole. We also present forums, events, projects and other exciting activities to the wider Victorian community.  Ausdance represents your interests at both a national and international level for dance development in Australia.  Through its political advocacy in Canberra,  its partnerships and national projects, such as the National Dance Forum, the Australian Dance Awards and the National Curriculum, it provides leadership for a strong and unified voice about dance in Australia.'),
