(248, 3, '2013-11-27 11:28:14', '2013-11-27 11:28:14', 'Etsy and the CAE invite you to contribute to an interactive art project in the CAE Info Shop. Get your craft on and join in building a progressive garland of white pom poms with our special guest instructors. Everyone will have the chance to be creative at any stage throughout the night so feel free to bring your family, partner or friends to participate in this collective workshop.', 'Pom Pom Project', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '116-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-27 11:28:14', '2013-11-27 11:28:14', '', 116, 'http://whitenight.dev/116-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
