(250, 3, '2013-11-28 04:06:49', '2013-11-28 04:06:49', 'The Southbank Pedestrian Bridge that leads to Southgate will be transformed into an immersive cocoon sparkling and flickering, delighting and enchanting audiences as they walk through.This light tunnel will be an extraordinary illumination in the centre of the river extending the creatively lit landscape of White Night Melbourne to the south.\r\n\r\nA White Night Melbourne Commission', 'Vortex', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'vortex-2', '', '', '2013-11-29 05:27:59', '2013-11-29 05:27:59', '', 0, 'http://whitenight.dev/?post_type=event&#038;p=250', 0, 'event', '', 0),
