(307, 3, '2013-11-27 13:22:55', '2013-11-27 13:22:55', 'Experience the arts precinct in a new light. Arts Centre Melbourne’s Hamer Hall will be open all night building on the encounters audiences experienced as part of White Night Melbourne 2013. Take a peek inside the recently refurbished building, an experience for art lovers from all walks of life. Programmed shows will be sure to pique curiosity.', 'Arts Centre Melbourne', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'arts-centre-melbourne', '', '', '2013-11-28 05:12:13', '2013-11-28 05:12:13', '', 0, 'http://whitenight.dev/?post_type=event&#038;p=307', 0, 'event', '', 0),
